Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.89,0:00:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}多數黨黨鞭辦公室  傑奎琳·A·夏普
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.61,0:00:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,換了名字真不習慣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Strange not seeing your name up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.54,0:00:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"改變即是進步"\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}"To improve is to change."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.14,0:00:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"常變即是求精"\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}"To perfect is to change often."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.95,0:00:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很熟悉丘吉爾的名言嘛\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You know your Churchill.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.61,0:00:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我離職去格蘭頓-希爾時  你送我的表上刻的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's inscribed on a watch you gave me when I left for Glendon Hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.38,0:00:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  禮物的事都是南茜安排\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Was it? Nancy arranges all the gifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.81,0:00:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她真瞭解你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She knows you well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.79,0:00:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我很喜歡跟你...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}As much as I am enjoying this little --
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.87,0:00:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我又爭取到兩票  帕崔奇和克勞斯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I got you two more votes. Partridge and Krauss.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.82,0:00:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷蒙德是在向我遞橄欖枝嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Is this Raymond's way of extending an olive branch?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.49,0:00:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算個開端吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's a start.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.23,0:00:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩票太少  算不上樹枝\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Two votes is a twig. It's not a branch.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.35,0:00:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我來了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Which is why I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.40,0:00:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五點開始投票  還剩不到三小時\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, the vote's at 5:00. We have less than three hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.04,0:00:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2小時49分鐘\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Two hours and forty-nine minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.62,0:00:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,足夠我們拉票了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We have made more happen in less.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.75,0:00:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我送的表嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Is that the watch?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.83,0:00:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是  比那個好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No. It's nicer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.10,0:00:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷蒙德為什麼改主意了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So, why did Raymond have a change of heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.86,0:00:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,政府停轉對誰都沒好處\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If the government grinds to a halt, that benefits no one.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.43,0:01:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們想讓總統專注於中國問題\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We want the President focused on China,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.10,0:01:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而不是為停轉和抗議分心\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}not distracted by furloughs and protests.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.43,0:01:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽傑奎琳的安排吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You take direction from Jacqueline.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.03,0:01:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她恐怕不會喜歡那樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She's not gonna like that very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.60,0:01:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不喜歡支使你嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Bossing you around?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.68,0:01:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不喜歡見我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Having me around.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.71,0:01:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不怪她\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Oh, I don't blame her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.37,0:01:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿什利會先問\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Ashleigh will start the interview with questions
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.31,0:01:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和丈夫的相識  早期的婚姻\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}about how you and your husband met, your early marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.50,0:01:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.36,0:01:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後會問一些關於你近況的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Then she'll move on to more specific questions
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.01,0:01:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,具體問題\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}about your recent transition.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.71,0:01:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.73,0:01:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她還要問你不要孩子的事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She's gonna ask about you having no children.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.38,0:01:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是說好不問這個嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I thought we'd agreed to take that off the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.26,0:01:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  但他們一定要問\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We did. But they insisted.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.36,0:01:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以直接找阿什利爭取\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Now I can speak to Ashleigh directly and fight for --
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.15,0:01:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事  以前也有人問過\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No. It's fine. I've been asked the question before.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.24,0:01:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道怎麼回答\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I know how to answer it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.34,0:01:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,儘可能短  不戳痛處\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It'll be quick and painless.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.44,0:01:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿什利來了我跟她確認一下\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And I'll confirm that with Ashleigh when she gets here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.64,0:01:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這件不錯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.50,0:01:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是別這麼中性化\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Maybe something less neutral.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.35,0:01:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你穿什麼都好看\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm sure you'll look good in whatever you choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.45,0:01:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去樓下等\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll be downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.07,0:01:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,狄所裡欠你的  你幫他搞定了天橋的資金\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Disori owes you -- for the overpass funding you secured.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.39,0:01:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}傾向同意  中立
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.82,0:01:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-沒錯    -我給他打電話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Yes, he does.   - I'll call him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.88,0:01:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,道格呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Where's Doug?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.75,0:01:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四處巡視  鞏固來之不易的勝利\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He's doing the rounds, making sure our hard-won stay hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.25,0:02:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,博奇和烏麥克也是  不過還是少15票\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Birch and Womack are doing the same. But we're still 15 short.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.18,0:02:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟他們都有聯繫\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Got relationships with most of these folks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.30,0:02:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,錢還不夠\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Money's not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.38,0:02:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我試過民主黨議會競選委員會撥款的路數了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I already tried the D-trip route.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.62,0:02:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,退休問題是關鍵對吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Retirement is the main sticking point, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.40,0:02:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老人也有投票權的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Old people vote.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.08,0:02:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去找退休人員協會  應該能減輕壓力\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll target the AARP. That'll take most of the heat off.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.07,0:02:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是浪費時間  我得去工作了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We're wasting our time. I gotta get to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.90,0:02:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帶上雷米吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Take Remy with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.63,0:02:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不該分頭行動嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Shouldn't we divide and conquer?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.29,0:02:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人更有說服力\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's harder to say "no" twice than once.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.76,0:02:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我儘量不礙事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll stay out of your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.83,0:02:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像《特拉華河流域法案》那次嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Like you did on the Watershed Act?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.27,0:02:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次我們在一邊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We're on the same side of the fence this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.81,0:02:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你來晚了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're late to the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.35,0:02:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就當雷米是你走投無路\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, think of Remy as the guy who shows up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.15,0:02:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給你雪中送炭的人吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}with a six-pack after the liquor store is closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.03,0:02:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來見誰\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Who's on your plate?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.42,0:02:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唐納德·布萊斯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Donald Blythe.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.98,0:02:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,見他不浪費時間嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Do you really think that's the best use of your time?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.88,0:02:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除非他能說服別人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If I can get him to turn his people.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.03,0:02:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼多雞蛋放一個籃子裡夠冒險的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's a lot of eggs to put in one basket.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.76,0:02:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可只有一個籃子\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We only have one basket.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.86,0:02:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傑奎琳  能借用你的辦公室嗎  我比較戀舊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Uh, Jacqueline, may I use your office, for old time's sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.72,0:02:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全聽副總統的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I serve at the pleasure of the Vice President.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.14,0:02:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2小時17分鐘\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Two hours and seventeen minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.11,0:03:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有時間和耐心通常就能說服唐納德·布萊斯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Normally, all I need to sway Donald Blythe is patience and time,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.30,0:03:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可現在我兩樣都沒有\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}neither of which I have right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.03,0:03:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時間不多了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Tick, tock.
