Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.30,0:04:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唐納德  你好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Donald. Good to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.96,0:04:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副總統先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mr. Vice President.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.95,0:04:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別客氣  叫弗蘭克吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Please, it's always "Frank" to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.08,0:04:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你找我  所以我來了  但我不會幫你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I came because you asked me, but don't mistake that for false hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.15,0:04:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抓緊時間去說服別人吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If you have other people to lobby, you should.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.06,0:04:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十分鐘\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.21,0:04:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無濟於事的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It won't change anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.41,0:05:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少喝杯咖啡  反正不要錢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, at the very least, enjoy the free coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.82,0:05:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不喝咖啡因飲料\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't drink caffeine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.07,0:05:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就脫咖啡因的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Then decaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.21,0:05:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不還是咖啡因嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Still has caffeine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.13,0:05:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就享受一下免費的氧氣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, enjoy the free oxygen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.59,0:05:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,眾議院辦公樓那邊待久了會悶\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's gets stuffy over there in the Longworth Building.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.00,0:05:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我來杯咖啡  然後\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Coffee for me, and, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.54,0:05:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,氣泡礦泉水  如果你們有的話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Seltzer water, if you have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.83,0:05:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們肯定有\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm sure we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.02,0:05:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你記仇的話  我很理解\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Now I can understand if you might hold a grudge.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.53,0:05:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不記仇  弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't hold grudges, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.63,0:05:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是不和本性虛偽的人談判\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I just don't negotiate with people who are fundamentally deceptive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.12,0:05:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我從來沒對你說過謊  唐納德\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I never lied to you, Donald.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.83,0:05:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你保證說要和我討論  結果你並沒有\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You promised to seek my counsel, which you never once did.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.64,0:05:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當時我們不得不把《教育法案》推到\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We had to move the education bill in a direction
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.99,0:05:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你不會喜歡的方向上去\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I knew would make you unhappy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.49,0:05:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我覺得不該去傷...    -你重創了工會的元氣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- I saw no reason to frustrate      - You eviscerated the unions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.28,0:05:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你把績效標準交由聯邦統一\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You federalized performance standards.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.02,0:05:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們要是不那麼做  法案就完蛋了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If we hadn't done that, the bill would've been dead in the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.29,0:05:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後現在你又想再繼續克扣你通過的那點資金\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And now you want to cut the pathetic level of funding you did manage to pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.47,0:05:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有點錢總比沒有好吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Isn't some funding better than none?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.21,0:05:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死了比變成植物人更能說明問題\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}A flat-line will send a louder message than life support.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.58,0:05:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽著  你湊出來的這個小同盟\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Look, I, I'm impressed with the little coalition
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.34,0:05:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,確實了不起\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}that you've cobbled together,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.37,0:05:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-但是我們    -也沒那麼小\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- But we      - Not so little.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.06,0:06:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,28票  你需要每一票\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Twenty-eight votes. And you need them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.20,0:06:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實一半就夠了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, really only half.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.42,0:06:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,零的一半還是零\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Half of zero is still zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.12,0:06:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓福利改革通過參議院\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I had to pull every trick in the book
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.85,0:06:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼手段都用了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}to get entitlement through the Senate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.32,0:06:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果眾議院沒通過  我們沒有再來的機會\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If it fails in the House, we don't get a round two.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.53,0:06:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是一錘子買賣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This is a one-time deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.92,0:06:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在參議院就不該通過\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It never should've passed the Senate to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.55,0:06:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們從頭開始好嗎  我可以向你道歉嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Can we start over? May I offer you an apology?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.38,0:06:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想聽  弗蘭克  我退出了《教育法案》\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Deaf ears, Frank. I withdrew myself from the education fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.26,0:06:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是我必須抗下的負擔\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and that is my cross to bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.21,0:06:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我一個錯誤絕不會犯兩次\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But I will be damned if I will make the same mistake twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.79,0:06:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這麼固執  淪落到茶黨的檔次上了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This sort of stubbornness makes you no better than the Tea Party.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.11,0:06:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只不過  我們是正確的一方\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Except for the fact that we happen to be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.25,0:06:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再坐幾分鐘  唐納德\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Just a few more minutes, Donald.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.44,0:06:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你水還都沒喝呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You haven't even had your seltzer yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.11,0:06:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們在東北部還有七個資料中心\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They have seven other data centers spread across the Northeast.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.04,0:06:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那希望太渺茫了吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Those aren't good odds.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.24,0:06:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我們能進入一個\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, if we can access one,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.57,0:06:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我應該就能和另七個通訊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I should be able to talk to the other seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.79,0:06:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它們都長那樣  像是核掩體裡的諾克斯堡\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And they all look like that, Fort Knox wrapped in a nuclear bunker.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.73,0:06:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們怎麼進去呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How do we get in?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.71,0:06:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是我們  是你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, we don't. You do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.08,0:07:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼進  我用什麼理由進\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How? Wh--what's my reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.99,0:07:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要寫一篇關於網路恐怖主義的文章  免費宣傳\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're writing a story on cyber terrorism. It's free publicity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.99,0:07:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果他們安保那麼嚴密\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But if they're so secure, I'm --
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.14,0:07:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們經常安排參觀  主要面向潛在客戶\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They give tours all the time, mostly to prospective clients.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.78,0:07:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你自己為什麼不去呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Then why haven't you done it yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.48,0:07:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我開了家網路安全公司\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Because I run a white-hat firm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.29,0:07:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我剛參觀完  那裡就遭入侵\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And if I were to show up in the tour logs before a breach,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.18,0:07:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會引起注意的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}it would raise alarms.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.57,0:07:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  我進去之後呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Okay, once I'm in?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.22,0:07:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伺服器都是這個樣子的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}These are what the servers look like.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.63,0:07:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你得進入隨便一個籠子裡\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're gonna get inside one of these cages.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.53,0:07:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你拿著這個  插到伺服器上\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You will have this. You slide it into the server.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.46,0:07:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-就這樣    -就這麼簡單嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Voila.      - It's that simple?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.73,0:07:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要做的就這些  我可不是  程式碼極端複雜\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yeah. Well, your part. Not mine. The code's extremely complex.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.97,0:07:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼做到這些還不被他們發現呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How do I do it without them noticing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.27,0:07:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和想要做好任何事一樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How you get good at anything:
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.01,0:07:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,熟能生巧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Practice makes perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.11,0:08:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出了個狀況\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We've got a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.32,0:08:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有人  停下手頭的工作  去最近的辦公室\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Everyone, stop what you're doing, head into the nearest office,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.69,0:08:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把門關上\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and shut the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.60,0:08:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你  原地不動\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You, stay exactly where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.59,0:08:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,退休年齡已經敲定了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Retirement age is a done deal,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.17,0:08:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我也許能撥一些款項去...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but I might be able to redistribute some appropriations to oth--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.41,0:08:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不是我想要的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's not what I'm after.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.02,0:08:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不能安個新輪轂罩就當修車了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You can't fix a wrecked car with new hubcaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.69,0:08:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個姊妹法案怎麼樣  完全針對教育問題\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How about a sister bill, one that focuses entirely on education.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.75,0:08:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的同盟是在為黨的尊嚴而戰\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}My coalition is fighting for the integrity of the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.65,0:08:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我們並不是隻注重教育    -不好意思  唐納德\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Tha- We're not just focused on Education.      - I'm sorry, Donald.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.35,0:08:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Excuse me for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.77,0:08:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,南茜  我說了  勿擾\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Nancy, I said, 'No interrup'—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.14,0:08:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}When?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.05,0:08:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但還有不到一小時就開始投票了  我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But the vote is in less than an hour. I
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.87,0:08:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不管什麼程式\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't care what protocol it--!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.51,0:08:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隔離  郵件中有白色粉末\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Quarantine. There's white powder in the mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.39,0:08:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們被關在這兒了嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We're locked in?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.20,0:08:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生  馬上把門關上\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Sir! Close the door now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.95,0:08:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽著  我必須\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Look, I have to --
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.77,0:08:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上  先生  請關門\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Now, sir! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.18,0:09:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得給我夫人打電話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I should call my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.17,0:09:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也得給克萊爾打個電話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And I should call Claire.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.05,0:09:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我應該告訴康納嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Should I tell Connor?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.36,0:09:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要  媒體最好不要知道\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No. It's better the press doesn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.28,0:09:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,檢測結果應該能在投票開始之前出\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The field tests should come in before the vote.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.08,0:09:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,投票結束我就回家\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And as soon as the tally's in, I'll come home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.83,0:09:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,情況怎麼樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How's it looking?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.03,0:09:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,挺危險  這次可能通不過\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Shaky. We may lose this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.22,0:09:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那採訪就難辦了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That could make for a tough interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.14,0:09:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我本來就不想接受採訪\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, I didn't want to do it in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.10,0:09:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在沒法後悔了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, we're committed now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.90,0:09:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得回去應付"聖十字軍"了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I better get back to the Holy Crusader.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.66,0:09:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,檢測一旦確認安全  就告訴我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let me know as soon as the tests have cleared.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.10,0:09:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果走運  是炭疽病毒\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If we're lucky, it'll be anthrax,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.54,0:09:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不用親眼看著法案不通過了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and I won't live long enough to see the bill fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.25,0:09:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.52,0:09:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會沒事的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We're gonna be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.19,0:09:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的隔離我們都經歷過多少次了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How many of these quarantines we been through?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.72,0:09:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都算不清了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I've lost count.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.18,0:09:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祝我能勸動唐納德吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Wish me luck with Donald.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.01,0:09:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,土地爺保佑\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Heels crossed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.26,0:09:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-黨團為此四分五裂    -當然\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- It's ripping the caucus apart.   - Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.25,0:09:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們要一起堅持用我們這版法案\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We take a united stand on our version of the bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.48,0:09:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們有些人得立場堅定\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Some of us have to stay on our feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.21,0:09:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事關黨內團結\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This is about party unity...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.98,0:09:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是讓我們放棄根基\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's about abandoning our base.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.86,0:09:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  凍結開銷才是動搖根基\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, that's what the Freeze is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.33,0:09:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刀兵相向對我們的根基沒什麼好處\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Our base doesn't benefit from sword-rattling.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.17,0:09:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只會搞得烏煙瘴氣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It gets left bleeding on the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.01,0:10:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的選區內的老年人數目在國內第三多\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}My district has the third largest number of seniors in the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.21,0:10:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果提高退休年齡  退休人員協會得吵翻天的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If we raise the age of retirement, the AARP will raise hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.84,0:10:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我今早和退休人員協會的主席談過\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I spoke with the President of the AARP this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.47,0:10:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他下週將收到一筆4500萬的捐款\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He'll be receiving a $45 million endowment next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.71,0:10:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,選民還是會抗議的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Voters will still revolt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.72,0:10:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中期選舉結果不會好看\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The midterms are gonna be ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.06,0:10:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}弗蘭克·安德伍德  國會封鎖  我困在這兒了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.46,0:10:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們很多人  當然也包括我...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Many of us – And I can certainly speak for myself – are fac --
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.48,0:10:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在的選擇是  政府立刻停擺\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The choice is between immediate discontinuation of services
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.56,0:10:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或是五年後提高退休年齡\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and an age bump five years from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.23,0:10:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是在拿假想的不適跟眼前的痛苦相比\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're comparing theoretical discomfort to imminent pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.20,0:10:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是覺得我們在跟核心價值觀背道而馳\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I just feel like we're losing touch with our core values.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.16,0:10:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,《教育法案》就是個很好的例子\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The Education Bill is a good example.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.97,0:10:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們跟著弗蘭克走\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We all followed Frank's lead,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.35,0:10:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望能靠他多少牽制一下共和黨\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}hoping it would buy us traction with the Republicans.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.71,0:10:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失陪一下  馬上回來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Would you excuse me, just one moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.56,0:10:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-媒體知道了嗎    -還不知道\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Does the press know?   - Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.24,0:10:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能和他保持聯繫嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Can you keep in touch with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.84,0:10:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得想辦法讓午餐賓客從命\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I need to pommel our lunch guests into submission.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.20,0:10:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你已經很接近了  放輕鬆  多聽\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You've got 'em close. But relax. Listen more.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.73,0:10:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們想要的是支援  而不是打擊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They want their hands held, not someone in their face.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.89,0:10:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道怎麼拉票\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I know how to whip votes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.14,0:11:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請享用特區最好的魚子醬  女士們先生們\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Best caviar in D.C., Ladies and Gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.01,0:11:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們怎麼能讓你付錢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We can't let you pay for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.52,0:11:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就別吃  如果吃了我也不會透露出去\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Then don't eat it. But if you do, I won't tell anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.68,0:11:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你剛剛說到《教育法案》是嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You were saying about the Education Bill?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.40,0:11:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  馬喬裡親愛的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, Marjory, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.43,0:11:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,記得嗎  我們剛剛才說過\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Remember, we just talked about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.71,0:11:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我剛剛在說...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I was telling you –
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.19,0:11:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對  沒什麼好擔心的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Right. Nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.26,0:11:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果有什麼疑問  就去問莫里\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If you have any questions, ask Molly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.34,0:11:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她知道怎麼回事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She knows what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.35,0:11:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道任何訊息就會馬上聯繫你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I will call as soon as I know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.33,0:11:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我愛你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.15,0:11:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬喬裡怎麼樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How's Marjory?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.59,0:11:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她還好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.01,0:12:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電話打得挺長\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Long call.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.45,0:12:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也知道  她情緒比較激動\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You know, she gets emotional.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.59,0:12:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫里休學了一個學期待在家裡\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Molly took a semester off to be at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.32,0:12:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我告訴她  春季必須回去\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I told her she needs to head back in the spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.20,0:12:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不希望她媽媽拖她後腿\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't want her mother dragging her down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.03,0:12:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真是不容易\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Must be hard on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.53,0:12:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得女兒們更不容易\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Harder on the girls, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.66,0:12:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-她意識清醒嗎    -一半時間是吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Is she lucid?   - About half the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.18,0:12:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勉強能明白自己惡化得多快\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Just enough to be aware of how quickly she's going.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.11,0:12:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真糟糕\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.60,0:12:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道我不該這麼說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I feel terrible saying it,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.77,0:12:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我心底更希望她別清醒過來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but part of me is looking forward to her not being lucid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.33,0:12:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少那樣她就不會知道發生了什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}At least then she won't realize what's happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.36,0:12:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我之前就該想到的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I should have thought of this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.21,0:12:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將心比心  而不是靠講道理\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Appeal to the heart, not the brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.78,0:12:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對這方面不太瞭解  但\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Forgive my ignorance, but
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.11,0:12:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這方面的研究有什麼進展嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}has there been any progress with research?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.67,0:13:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一些  基因測試  血管改造  但進展很慢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Some. Genetic testing, vascular manipulation, but it's slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.87,0:13:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬喬裡趕不上這些研究的成果了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They won't come up with anything in time for Marjory.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.46,0:13:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們只想提高生活質量\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We're focusing on quality of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.02,0:13:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽著  我知道你還有事  我...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Look, I -- I know you have work to do, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.57,0:13:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經不是黨鞭了  那是傑奎琳的工作\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Oh, I'm no longer the Whip anymore. That's Jacqueline's job.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.65,0:13:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我同意見你  是因為我們有交情\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I just agreed to meet with you because we have a history.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.65,0:13:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她很難拒絕吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She would be tougher to say not to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.71,0:13:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-但還是該拒絕的    -沒錯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- But still it would've been a "no".   - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.39,0:13:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我佩服你的信念  唐納德\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I admire your convictions, Donald.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.23,0:13:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如今像你這樣的人鳳毛麟角了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're a rare breed nowadays.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.92,0:13:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你拿我們跟茶黨比的時候  可不是這麼說的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It didn't sound that way when you were comparing us to the Tea Party.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.58,0:13:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不該那麼說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I was being unfair.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.60,0:13:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是反動派  是進步分子\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're not a reactionary. You're a progressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.70,0:13:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白你的意思\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I see where this is going.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.13,0:13:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.47,0:13:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我坐了這麼久冷板凳\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}When you've been in the wasteland as long as I have,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.62,0:13:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對奉承已經有免疫力了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}you become immune to flattery.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.15,0:13:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你認為我是個本性虛偽的人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I know you think I'm fundamentally deceptive,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.66,0:13:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我也能真誠地讚美別人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but I am capable of a genuine compliment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.68,0:13:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就謝謝你了  但這不會動搖我的決心\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Then I will take it as one, but it won't soften my resolve.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.18,0:13:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然  否則你就配不上這讚美了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If it did, you wouldn't deserve the compliment in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.23,0:13:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你投了反對票  我也不會指責你們\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If you vote ':no,' I won't hold it against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.49,0:14:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們一條陣線的  中期選舉也是\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We're all in this together through the midterms.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.90,0:14:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但如果你們跟我走\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But if you stick with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.51,0:14:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們就讓共和黨和美國人民知道\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}we can show both the Republicans and the American people
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.52,0:14:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不是就會鬧僵\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}that we are capable of more than stagnation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.11,0:14:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是很重要的  就算會有些痛苦\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And that's worth something, even it if hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.89,0:14:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們誰跟我走\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Who can I count on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.68,0:14:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,收到\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Copy that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.38,0:14:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們之間還隔著道門  我猜不是好兆頭\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The fact that there is still a door between us, I take as a bad sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.79,0:14:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一份樣本檢測呈陰性  一份不確定  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}One tested negative, one inconclusive, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.22,0:14:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們必須把樣本帶回實驗室\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That means we have to take the samples to the lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.12,0:14:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那還要多久\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So, how much longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.39,0:15:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還需要三四個小時吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Another three or four hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.07,0:15:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們有一項重要投票要舉行\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We have an important vote going to the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.13,0:15:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我必須跟我的人談談\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I have to be talking to my people.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.17,0:15:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,投票已經延期了  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The vote is delayed, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.79,0:15:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們正在疏散國會大廈這一側\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We're evacuating this side of the Capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.71,0:15:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不投票了嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So no vote?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.94,0:15:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我們確認沒問題之前不會投票了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Not until we get the all-clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.82,0:15:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好人有好報\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Good things happen to good people.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.57,0:15:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有一件事  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Another thing, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.24,0:15:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有的手機服務  無線網  座機\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}All cell phone service, Wi-Fi, land lines --
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.67,0:15:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們都會封鎖  以防可能安全威脅\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We'll be blocking them, in case there's a legitimate security threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.70,0:15:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得跟我妻子保持聯繫\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I need to be able to call my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.90,0:15:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  先生  我們可以找人通知她\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I apologize, sir. We can have someone notify her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.96,0:15:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  必須是我才行\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No. It needs to be me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.22,0:15:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是陌生的聲音  會讓她非常緊張\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She gets very anxious if she doesn't recognize the voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.97,0:15:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,議員先生  我被嚴令禁止...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Congressman, I have strict instructions not to allo—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.93,0:15:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想辦法解決  除非你想讓我把白宮扯進來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Figure it out. Unless you want me to get the White House involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.04,0:15:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會想辦法的  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll find a way, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.16,0:15:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當副總統還是有好處的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There are advantages to being Vice President.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.08,0:15:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女士  我們得要求你暫時留在這裡\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Ma'am? We'll have to ask you to remain up here for a little while.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.63,0:15:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是因為隔離嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Is it the quarantine?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.73,0:15:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,國會大廈正在疏散\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The Capitol is being evacuated.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.46,0:15:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該不會有問題\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We expect everything to be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.64,0:15:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是標準程式\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's just standard procedure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.41,0:16:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你打不通的  通訊中斷了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Uh, you won't be able to get through. Communication is being jammed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.37,0:16:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒法跟弗蘭西斯通話嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You mean I can't even speak to Francis?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.44,0:16:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,確認安全之前不行\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Not until the all-clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.50,0:16:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要多久\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How long?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.44,0:16:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在估計要四小時\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Four hours is the estimate right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.16,0:16:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,25分鐘後就要錄影了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We're supposed to tape it in 25 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.03,0:16:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們無能為力\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Nothing we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.02,0:16:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還好嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.54,0:16:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.19,0:16:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去找艾瑪談談\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll go talk to Emma.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.61,0:16:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事了  謝謝你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You know, I'm fine. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.24,0:16:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾瑪\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Em.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.49,0:16:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們可能有點問題\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So we might have a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.74,0:16:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新聞裡都報道了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's all over the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.08,0:16:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能還要一陣子\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It could be a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.99,0:16:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們能通過音訊採訪副總統嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Can we get audio from the Vice President?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.62,0:16:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在疏散結束之前通訊都是中斷的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Communications are being jammed until the evacuation is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.49,0:16:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你跟阿什利談過了嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Have you spoken to Ashleigh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.43,0:16:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她覺得我們該弄輛轉播車來  回頭直播\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She thinks we should get a sat truck down here. Wait and go live.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.84,0:16:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒法保證什麼時候能恢復\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I can't guarantee when that will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.58,0:16:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副總統被隔離在國會大廈  我們有獨家新聞\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The Vice President is quarantined in the Capitol, and we have an exclusive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.47,0:16:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管我們何時開工  電視臺都會轉播的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The network will broadcast whenever the hell we tell them to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.46,0:16:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們會等你到達\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They're holding off until you get here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.23,0:16:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你應該獨自做採訪\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You should do the interview solo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.72,0:16:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想等你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'd rather wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.77,0:16:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道我們能不能贏得投票\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Who knows whether we'll win the vote?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.54,0:16:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我們輸了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If we lose,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.36,0:16:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想上全國電視臺\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't want my face on national television.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.20,0:16:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這或許也是好事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This could be a silver lining.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.13,0:16:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道  弗蘭西斯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't know, Francis.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.69,0:17:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你肯定會很棒的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm sure you'll be terrific.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.74,0:17:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟康納商量一下吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let me run it past Connor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.11,0:17:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的  謝謝  我們說完了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Okay. Thank you. We're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.54,0:17:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生  我們接通了布萊斯太太\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Sir, we were able to get Mrs. Blythe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.87,0:17:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唐納德\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Oh, Donald...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.38,0:17:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬喬裡\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Marjory?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.91,0:17:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-喂    -對  是我  親愛的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Hello?   - Yes, it's me, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.56,0:17:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽不清你說話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's hard to hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.06,0:17:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們還被困在辦公室裡\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We're still stuck inside the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.64,0:17:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼辦公室\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What office?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.97,0:17:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在國會大廈  還得要一陣子\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}At the Capitol. It --it's going to be a l—a little while longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.35,0:17:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你為什麼去那裡  今天是星期天啊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But why are you there? It's Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.75,0:17:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  今天是星期五  親愛的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, it -- it's Friday, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.11,0:17:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-唐納德    -我在呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Donald?   - I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.68,0:17:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我在一起的男人是誰\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Uh, who is this man with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.55,0:17:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是一位警察\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Uh, he's a police officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.39,0:17:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們用對講機讓我們通話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They're using walkie-talkies so we can speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.25,0:17:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在跟誰說話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Who am I talking to?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.85,0:17:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是您丈夫  夫人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's your husband, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.16,0:17:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒結婚\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm not married.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.18,0:17:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我  是唐納德\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It -- It's me. It's Donald.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.32,0:17:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關上  我不認識那個那人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Turn it off. I don't know that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.32,0:17:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬喬裡\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Marjory...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.55,0:17:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她去另一個房間了  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She went into the other room, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.34,0:17:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的  謝謝\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Okay. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.28,0:17:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能麻煩你陪著她嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If you could stay with her, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.29,0:17:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.20,0:18:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喝一杯嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.85,0:18:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Sure. Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.60,0:18:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他可能要到午夜才有空\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}For all we know it could be midnight before he's out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.32,0:18:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後他還要主持投票\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And then he still needs to manage the vote.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.79,0:18:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凌晨兩點我們也沒問題\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We're fine if it's two a.m.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.05,0:18:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都睡著的時候播嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}When everyone's asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.08,0:18:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人們會為這個熬夜的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}People would stay up for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.44,0:18:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關鍵就是想在黃金時段播\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The whole point was prime time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.90,0:18:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我們明天再進行\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Then we do it tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.95,0:18:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經為這個推掉半天的日程了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We've already set aside half a day for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.64,0:18:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副總統先生不會為一個訪談重新安排一整天的日程\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The Vice President can't rearrange his entire schedule for an interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.05,0:18:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,眼下也沒有其他的選擇\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't see any other options.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.94,0:18:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和弗蘭西斯用對講談過了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I spoke to Francis over the radio.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.05,0:18:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們認為應該我單獨接受採訪\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We think I should do it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.24,0:18:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有你一人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Just you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.86,0:18:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安德伍德夫人和阿什利  一對一\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mrs. Underwood and Ashleigh, one-on-one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.95,0:18:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許我們可以轉播他的錄音\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Maybe we can broadcast his voice
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.12,0:18:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗蘭西斯不希望訪談完全是關於隔離的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Francis doesn't want the entire interview to be about the quarantine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.18,0:19:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也一樣  那隻是個小插曲\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Neither do I. That's just spectacle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.11,0:19:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隔離是新聞  這是難得的機會\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The quarantine is news. We have a unique opportunity --
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.90,0:19:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那好  我們取消吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Fine. We're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.95,0:19:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-什麼    -取消訪談  不重新安排\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- What?      - Cancel the interview. No reschedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.79,0:19:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣  康納\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Come on, Connor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.47,0:19:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你收拾好東西離開\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Please pack up everything and leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.62,0:19:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  我給阿什利打電話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Okay, wait. Let me call Ashleigh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.95,0:19:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以為我會逐漸習慣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I thought I'd get used to it,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.96,0:19:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我沒有  每次還是很痛苦\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but no. Hurts every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.50,0:19:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和一個人一起生活了三十年\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You spend 30 years with someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.81,0:19:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而現在她甚至不知道你是誰\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and then they don't have a damn clue who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.84,0:19:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的不應該\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Ugh... I really shouldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.43,0:19:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我們不該做的事就不做\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If we never did anything we shouldn't do,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.20,0:19:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就體會不到做該做的事的成就感了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}we'd never feel good about doing the things we should.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.89,0:19:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說的好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Excellent point.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.52,0:19:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果這是我們生命最後的時刻\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And if these are our last moments on earth
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.67,0:19:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道你怎麼打算  我倒寧願喝醉了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't know about you, but I'd rather go out with a buzz on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.21,0:19:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敬馬喬裡\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}To Marjory.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.23,0:19:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你非常愛她\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You love her dearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.70,0:19:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勝過其他一切\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}More than anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.77,0:19:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不敢想像沒有克萊爾我會怎麼辦\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I can't imagine what I'd do without Claire,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.00,0:20:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或是如果她記不起我是誰\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}or if she didn't remember who I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.04,0:20:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但願你不會遇到這樣的情況\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Hopefully, you'll never have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.33,0:20:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可你  或是任何人遇上這種事都讓我覺得生氣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, it makes me angry that you do, that anybody does.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.07,0:20:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒必要為你不能改變的事而生氣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No sense being angry over what you can't change.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.99,0:20:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老年癡呆的研究有多少經費\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How much funding does Alzheimer's research get?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.99,0:20:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不到五億\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Just under $500 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.43,0:20:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是專家  但這個數聽上去有點少啊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, I'm no expert, but that sounds inadequate to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.36,0:20:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,確實是  如果分配一百塊用於研究\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It is. For every $100 we allocate to research,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.08,0:20:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就得花將近三萬用於看護\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}we spend nearly $30,000 on care.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.14,0:20:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得改變這種情況\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We oughta change that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.47,0:20:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我試過了  我的法案都沒通過委員會\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I tried. My bill didn't even leave committee.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.54,0:20:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰反對\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Who opposed it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.45,0:20:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,霍華德·韋伯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Howard Webb.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.65,0:20:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,撥款委員會的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Ugh. Appropriations.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.31,0:20:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他都沒讓法案投票\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He didn't even put it to a vote.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.89,0:20:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我向來不喜歡霍華德\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I've never been fond of Howard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.77,0:20:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也一樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That makes two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.58,0:20:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的原因是什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What was his argument?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.39,0:20:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他覺得他不欠我的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He didn't feel he owed me one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.00,0:20:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"浪費開銷"  他就說了這一句\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}'Fiscally irresponsible,' is all he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.26,0:20:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我好好說說你的法案\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Walk me through the specifics of your bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.10,0:21:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你要幹什麼了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I see what you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.73,0:21:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Doing what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.96,0:21:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真讓人噁心  弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're disgusting, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.57,0:21:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.68,0:21:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,利用我妻子\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Using my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.11,0:21:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唐納德  你在說什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Donald, what are saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.50,0:21:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以為你多給老年癡呆一點研究經費\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You think I'll give in on Entitlement
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.98,0:21:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就會在福利改革修正案上妥協\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}if you slap some extra Alzheimer's funding on the table?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.20,0:21:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我完全沒這個意思\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I was not suggesting that at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.19,0:21:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡說  弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Bullshit, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.36,0:21:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以隨便看低我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You think as little of me as you want,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.18,0:21:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我不拿健康作交易籌碼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but I do not barter with people's health.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.01,0:21:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你為什麼要上調退休年限\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Then why are you trying to raise the age of Retirement?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.23,0:21:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,醫療研究  我們負擔得起\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Medical research we can afford.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.98,0:21:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,醫療保險  我們負擔不起  這是現實  唐納德\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Medicare, we can't. There are realities, Donald.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.38,0:21:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別和我談什麼現實  我妻子在漸漸死去\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Don't talk down to me about reality. My wife is dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.76,0:21:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這才是現實  如果你的法案通過\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's a reality. Other people will die, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.10,0:21:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有其他人會死  這才是現實\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}if your package succeeds. That's a reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.59,0:21:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該死的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}God damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.34,0:21:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真希望我沒跟你一起困在這兒\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I wish I wasn't stuck in this fucking room with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.75,0:21:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唐納德\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Donald?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.35,0:21:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再說什麼了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm done talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.54,0:21:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-再來一次    -我能行\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- One more time.   - I've got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.21,0:21:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望聽起來更自然\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I want it to sound more natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.56,0:21:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗蘭西斯和我獻身公共事業\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Uh, Francis and I both wanted to devote our lives to public service.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.04,0:21:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我們一致認為投身公職\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And we didn't feel that we could both do that
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.45,0:21:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就難以善盡父母之責\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and be the parents we wanted to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.34,0:22:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們作了取捨  讓我們有更多時間\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And by making that choice it allows more time for us
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.45,0:22:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為其他人服務\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}to be in the service of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.84,0:22:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好  聽起來很好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Good. That sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.18,0:22:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請過來吧  安德伍德夫人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We need you, Mrs. Underwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.49,0:22:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓德里克待在國會大廈\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Keep Derek at the Capitol.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.61,0:22:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,採訪被疏散者和國土安全部\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I want quotes from evacuees and Homeland Security.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.07,0:22:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓薩拉完成生化威脅歷史的部分\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And Sarah should be finishing that history of biohazard scares.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.81,0:22:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很快就過去\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll be there soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.35,0:22:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要走了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.89,0:22:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行  我們還沒幹完\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No. We're not done yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.31,0:22:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是個大新聞  我明天再過來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This is a major story. I'll come back tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.86,0:22:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣你就是連續兩天都是如此  這就有了規律\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Gonna be two days in a row, and this is how patterns emerge.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.73,0:22:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聯調局喜歡規律  我們不能去撞槍口\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The FBI likes patterns, and we do not give the FBI what the FBI likes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.51,0:22:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能一整天都消失  現在正是...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I can't disappear all day in the middle of –
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.43,0:22:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有八個記者正在外面跑新聞\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I have eight reporters out in the field,okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.09,0:22:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別說了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.62,0:22:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我  我為什麼要買腰果\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Tell me why I purchased Cashew.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.51,0:22:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.07,0:22:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了陪伴我嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Companionship?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.91,0:22:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.50,0:22:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更重要的是  提醒我自己\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}More importantly, a reminder that I am never
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.28,0:22:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我距離被關進籠子裡只有一步之遙\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}more than one wrong move away from life in a cage.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.91,0:23:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你留下來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.56,0:23:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我讓你看看我要寫的全部程式碼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll walk you through every line of code I intend to write,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.20,0:23:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我每一次對防火牆的攻擊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}every attempt I make to breach the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.52,0:23:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我們被抓  你不能說自己一無所知\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If we get caught, you don't get to plead ignorance.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.44,0:23:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們一起進去\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We go down together.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.42,0:23:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  我不是來玩雌雄大盜的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, I didn't sign up for Bonnie and Clyde.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.73,0:23:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你需要我做這一件事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You need me for this one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.88,0:23:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也需要你  但無論我來之前你做了什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Just like I need you. But whatever you've done before me, that --
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.05,0:23:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我住在哪裡  你知道我是誰\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You know where I live. And you know who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.99,0:23:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐下  我們越早開始  就能越早結束\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Sit down. The sooner we start, the sooner we finish.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.50,0:23:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,國會大廈依然封鎖  防化部隊成員\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The Capitol is still on lockdown, as HAZMAT crews
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.39,0:23:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還在繼續檢查整棟大廈\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}continue a thorough sweep of the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.85,0:23:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天早上  一封寄給多數黨黨鞭\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Earlier this morning, a white powder-like substance...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.61,0:23:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傑奎琳·夏普的包裹中\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}...was found in a package mailed to the office
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.07,0:23:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發現了白色粉末狀物質\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}of Majority Whip Jacqueline Sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.00,0:23:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在可以走了嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Not are we free to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.52,0:23:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快了  不到一小時\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Almost, sir. Less than hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.80,0:23:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有一條你太太發來的訊息\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I've got a message from your wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.45,0:23:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼訊息\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.52,0:23:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她正在做現場採訪\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She's doing the interview live right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.80,0:23:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與議員唐納德·布萊斯及夏普女士手下\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}...Quarantined with Congressman Donald Blythe
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.36,0:24:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十四名員工隔離在一起  特情局...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and 14 of Miss Sharp's staff. The secrets
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.24,0:24:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安德伍德夫人  我非常感激你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mrs. Underwood, I so appreciate you taking the time to speak
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.78,0:24:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能在今天這種情況下與我們對話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}with us today in what, I am certain,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.34,0:24:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你現在一定很擔心\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}is a very stressful situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.00,0:24:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  阿什利\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you, Ashleigh.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.39,0:24:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你今天跟你丈夫通過話嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Have you spoken with your husband today?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.28,0:24:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  他狀態很不錯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes, I did. And he's in very good spirits,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.85,0:24:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特情局處理的很好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and in good hands with the Secret Service.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.65,0:24:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然  對於不能來他感到很失望\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Of course, he's very disappointed he couldn't be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.64,0:24:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的心與他同在\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, our thoughts are with him and --
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.07,0:24:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及被隔離在國會大廈的所有人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and everyone quarantined at the Capitol.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.59,0:24:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.57,0:24:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想要你在德克薩斯州\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'd like to begin with Claire Underwood
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.35,0:24:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遇到你丈夫之前開始說起\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}before she met her husband, in Texas.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.95,0:24:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有一些照片\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And I have a couple of pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.73,0:24:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-不會吧    -是的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Oh, no.   - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.56,0:24:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天吶  那是紅鬃\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Oh. My goodness. That was Red.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.85,0:24:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是個熟練的騎手嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}An accomplished rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.34,0:24:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,狂熱的騎手\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Uh, an enthusiast.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.84,0:24:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這張是幾年以後的照片\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This one's from a couple of years later.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.45,0:24:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天吶\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Oh, my goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.38,0:24:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡這雙皮便鞋嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You like those penny loafers?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.73,0:24:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妙極了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Those are wonder—
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.67,0:24:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是兩個截然不同的女孩\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Those are two very different girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.84,0:24:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你更喜歡做哪一個\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Which one are you more comfortable being?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.17,0:25:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我家的農場  那是我的家園\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}My family's ranch. That was home…for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.71,0:25:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不喜歡預科學校嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You didn't like the prep school?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.67,0:25:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  我想我更喜歡泥巴\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No. I think I preferred the dirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.73,0:25:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你在達拉斯長大  在高地公園\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You grew up in – in Dallas, though. Um, Highland Park.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.79,0:25:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我父親  他是個生意人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes. My father, um, well, he was a businessman,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.86,0:25:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們住在城裡  但我們是農場主\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So we lived in the city, but we're ranchers.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.40,0:25:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們家過去三代人都是\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I mean, we – we go back three generations, our family.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.43,0:25:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你父母非常有錢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Your parents were very wealthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.47,0:25:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們過得很舒坦  沒錯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Uh, we were comfortable, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.47,0:25:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們讓我應有盡有\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They made sure I wanted for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.69,0:25:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的確是個快樂的童年\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It was a very happy childhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.40,0:25:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那段時間你最鮮活的記憶是什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What is your most vivid memory from that time?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.81,0:25:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我"最鮮活的記憶"\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}My 'most vivid memory.'
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.11,0:25:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能是我九歲或十歲的時候\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Probably when I was about nine or ten,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.88,0:25:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我父親帶我去了肯尼迪遇刺的迪利廣場\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}my father took me to Dealey Plaza, where Kennedy was shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.79,0:25:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他說"克萊爾  一位偉人死在這裡"\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And he said, 'Claire, a great man died here.'
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.99,0:26:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我記得我當時還不完全理解死亡的概念\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And I remember not fully comprehending the meaning of death yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.64,0:26:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我問他總統怎麼死的  他就跟我說了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And I asked him how he died, and he told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.28,0:26:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我記得我感到十分難過和憤怒\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And I remember feeling so sad, so angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.78,0:26:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這太不公平了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It seemed so unfair.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.31,0:26:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我哭了起來  然我後父親抱起我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I started to cry, and my daddy picked me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.74,0:26:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他用胳膊摟著我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And he wrapped his arms around me,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.96,0:26:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後說道  "別傷心  寶貝兒\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and he said, 'Don't be sad, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.29,0:26:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他讓世界變得更好了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}"He made the world a better place,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.54,0:26:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但有時這是要付出代價的"\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but sometimes that comes at a price.'
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.76,0:26:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想這就是我最鮮活的記憶了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I guess that was the most vivid memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.69,0:26:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們就差八票了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We are only eight votes away.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.69,0:26:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我心意已決\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry. I've made up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.15,0:26:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也一樣  我得堅持立場\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Me, too. I've gotta stick to my guns on this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.74,0:27:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們寧願讓政府關門...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You would rather let the government shut down --
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.31,0:27:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你注意點\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Hey, hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.42,0:27:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這你怨不著我們\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Don't put that on us
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.59,0:27:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰叫黨鞭大人最後才想起來我們\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}just because we're on the ass-end of the whip list.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.50,0:27:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別誤會  我們都很敬重你  傑姬\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Don't get us wrong. We have a lot of respect for you Jackie.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.02,0:27:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗蘭克升任之後你一直幹得不錯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're doing a fine job since Frank's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.96,0:27:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許風格不同  但還是很好的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Different styles, but a fine job.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.66,0:27:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請諸位稍候片刻\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Excuse us just a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.75,0:27:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們根本不拿我當回事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They're not taking me seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.09,0:27:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你不是弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}'Cause you're not Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.55,0:27:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是說我不是個男人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You mean because I'm not a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.85,0:27:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  我就是說弗蘭克  他們都習慣了做交易\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No. I mean Frank. They're used to being offered something.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.42,0:27:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,問問他們有什麼要求\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Ask them what they want.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.46,0:27:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道保羅在垃圾處理廠的事上需要幫忙\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I know Paul needs help with a waste treatment facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.32,0:27:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也和他們一樣瞧不起我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're being just as condescending as they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.82,0:27:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有好建議送到眼前  就接受吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Take some good advice when you get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.16,0:27:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我之前就說對了  是不是\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I was right earlier, wasn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.31,0:27:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保羅  雷米告訴我你需要一間垃圾處理廠\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Paul, Remy tells me you need a waste treatment plant.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.94,0:27:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們在申請聯邦基金方面是有點麻煩\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We've had some trouble getting matching federal funds.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.57,0:27:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本  你說你想在選區裡蓋一座葡萄酒博物館\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Ben, you mentioned once a winery museum in your district?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.37,0:27:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們長島如今的葡萄酒是很不錯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We are making some great wines in Long Island these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.24,0:27:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喝過啊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I've tried some.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.54,0:27:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟納帕[著名酒鄉]產的比起來難喝得要死\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It tastes like piss, compared to what we have in Napa,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.39,0:28:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種東西正好該送進保羅的垃圾處理廠\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}the sort of piss that belongs in Paul's waste treatment plant.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.32,0:28:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傑姬\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Jackie--
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.10,0:28:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們剛遭遇了一場疑似恐怖襲擊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We have a possible terror attack,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.37,0:28:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而你們還在這持票待沽\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and you're holding out your plate for more pork.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.16,0:28:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們真該為自己感到羞愧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You should be ashamed of yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.67,0:28:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我治下黨團  黨員只會因優異表現受嘉獎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}In my caucus, people are rewarded for good behavior,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.27,0:28:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會鼓勵拿選票換酬金\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}not trading their votes for ransom.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.98,0:28:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,待會兒進去投票  你們兩位都要投贊成\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}When we walk in there, I expect the both of you to vote 'yes,'
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.01,0:28:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且要毫不猶豫\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}without a moment's hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.59,0:28:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多謝兩位心意回轉\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you for your change of heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.13,0:28:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只剩六票了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Six more to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.59,0:28:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你離開德州  在著名的菲利普斯學院\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You left Texas and, um, spent the last two years of high school
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.19,0:28:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,度過了中學最後兩年\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}at the prestigious Phillips Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.46,0:28:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後考進了拉德克利夫學院\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Um, and then, onto Radcliffe. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.15,0:28:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}哈佛大學兩個本科生院之一  專收女生
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.57,0:28:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是在那兒  你邂逅了未來的美國副總統\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Where you would meet the future Vice President.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.91,0:28:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他那時只是個帥氣的法學院學生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Back then just a dashing law student.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.99,0:28:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我從沒想到過他會成為副總統\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I never dreamed he would become Vice President, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.08,0:28:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人認為你們的婚姻比你說的要\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Some people might think that your marriage may be a bit more
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.81,0:28:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有更多的算計\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}calculated than you let on,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.32,0:28:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許他用得上你家的財富\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}that perhaps he needed your family's money.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.99,0:29:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是這樣的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No. That's just not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.41,0:29:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你父親可是為他的競選投入不菲\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Your father did contribute an awful lot to his campaign.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.95,0:29:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  因為他相信弗蘭西斯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes, he did. Because he believed in Francis.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.65,0:29:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有你父親的資助\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Would he have won that campaign
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.90,0:29:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他還能贏得選舉嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}had it not been for your father's contributions?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.99,0:29:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這我不清楚  我父親的資助絕對起了作用\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't know. I mean, it certainly helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.16,0:29:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我認為  是弗蘭西斯的理念和領導力\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But I like to think that it was Francis' ideas and leadership
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.02,0:29:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說服了選民  而不僅僅是競選廣告\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}that convinced voters, not just TV commercials.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.31,0:29:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和副總統已結婚27年了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You've been married for 27 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.47,0:29:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.65,0:29:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們結婚時還在上學  那時你們都很年輕\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You were just in school. I mean, you married so young.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.15,0:29:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  但如果找到了真愛\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We did. But when you've found 'the one'…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.05,0:29:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗蘭西斯就是我的真愛\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}well, Francis was the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.39,0:29:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你稱呼他為"弗蘭西斯"\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You call him "Francis."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.35,0:29:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在老家  他們還是叫他"弗蘭克"\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, back home, they call him "Frank," still.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.11,0:29:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他喜歡我叫他"弗蘭西斯"\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But he likes that I call him "Francis."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.47,0:29:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他說這稱呼讓他顯得更老成\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He said it makes him sound more sophisticated.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.29,0:29:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當政治家的妻子難嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Is it hard being a politician's wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.48,0:29:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,令人興奮  但也有難處\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's thrilling. Not without its challenges.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.35,0:29:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甘居幕後  為了他的追求而委屈自己\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Always in the background, subsuming your goals for his goals.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.35,0:29:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我倒不這麼看\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, I don't see it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.72,0:30:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們都是非常獨立的人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We're two very independent people who
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.44,0:30:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是選擇共同經營生活而已\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}have chosen to live our lives together.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.12,0:30:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我支援他 他也支援我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I support him. He supports me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.63,0:30:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就回到了政治上的合作的話題上\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Which, you know, goes back to the political partnership.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.45,0:30:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我丈夫的確是位政治家\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, my husband happens to be a politician,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.44,0:30:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我也正好從事政治工作\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and I happen to do political work.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.11,0:30:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我們的關係遠不止如此\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But our partnership extends far beyond that.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.49,0:30:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孩子呢  這是你們做的犧牲嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Children. Was that a sacrifice?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.98,0:30:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你們還沒生過孩子\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Because you haven't had any.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.88,0:30:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗蘭西斯和我獻身公共事業\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Francis and I wanted to devote our lives to public service.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.21,0:30:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我們一致認為投身公職\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And we didn't feel that we could both do that
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.79,0:30:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就難以善盡父母之責\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and be the parents we wanted to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.91,0:30:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們作了取捨\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So, we made the choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.68,0:30:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這回答我們之前聽過了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We've heard that answer before.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.76,0:30:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Sorry?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.57,0:30:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在以前的訪問中給出過一模一樣的回答\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You have given the exact same answer in previous interviews.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.97,0:30:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這是事實\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Because it's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.78,0:30:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  但是"工作"和"時機"\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Forgive me, but 'career' and 'timing,'
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.22,0:30:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人們總會找這樣的藉口\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}uh, those are often very convenient answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.78,0:30:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從有這個念頭到真正去做之間有個過程\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It is true that whatever it takes for people to get
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.59,0:31:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我一直沒能走完這個過程\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}from 'maybe' to 'yes' never arrived for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.69,0:31:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不覺得有壓力嗎  沒有做母親的渴望嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Never felt the pressure? No maternal instinct?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.94,0:31:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.40,0:31:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼這是你的選擇  並不是你不能生育\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And it was a choice? It wasn't because you couldn't have any?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.10,0:31:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗蘭西斯和我是為了大局著想\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, Francis and I did what was right for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.61,0:31:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為即使是現在\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Because it is unusual, I mean, even now,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.07,0:31:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身在領導層的政治家沒有孩子\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}for politicians at the executive level
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.81,0:31:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是不尋常的事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}not to have children.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.99,0:31:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.03,0:31:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你丈夫第二次參加國會競選時\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}In your husband's second congressional campaign,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.82,0:31:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一位反墮胎的共和黨候選人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}there was a Republican, a pro-family candidate,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.64,0:31:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他對你們做了一些相當難聽的指責\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}who made some pretty unsettling accusations.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.09,0:31:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗蘭西斯是一位南方的民主黨人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, Francis is a Southern Democrat,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.17,0:31:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我倆的臉皮都很厚\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and we have thick skins.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.25,0:31:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他說  為了保住你丈夫的政治生涯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He suggested, in order to keep your husband's political career on track.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.84,0:31:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孩子是很多人生活的中心\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Children are the center of many people's lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.63,0:31:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我認為他們只是想確保\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And I think they just want to make sure that
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.04,0:31:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,選出的代表會為了他們孩子的未來奮鬥\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}their representatives will fight for their children's dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.14,0:31:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而弗蘭西斯已經一次又一次地證明了自己\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And Francis has, again and again, proven that he will.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.40,0:32:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作為副總統他也會繼續做出努力\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And he will continue to do as Vice President.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.90,0:32:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他還聲稱在競選時你可能已經懷孕\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He claimed that you may have been pregnant during the campaign.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.30,0:32:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你當時懷孕了嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Was there a pregnancy?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.61,0:32:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你懷過孕嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Have you ever been pregnant?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.97,0:32:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-馬上停播    -不行\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Break. Now.   - That's not gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.52,0:32:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,懷過\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.34,0:32:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在競選期間嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}During the campaign?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.95,0:32:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之前\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Before.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.29,0:32:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是流產了嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Was it a miscarriage?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.54,0:32:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.25,0:32:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你終止妊娠了嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Did you – did you terminate the pregnancy?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.65,0:32:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我說"是"\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If I said 'yes,'
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.98,0:32:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我丈夫的政治生涯就會面臨危險\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}my husband's political career would be in jeopardy.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.17,0:32:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我信仰會遭質疑\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}My faith would be questioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.73,0:32:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同樣  我的生活也會受到威脅\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Likely, my life would be threatened.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.43,0:33:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我不會感到羞恥  是的  我懷過孕\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But I won't be ashamed. Yes, I was pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.12,0:33:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且是的  我墮過胎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And, yes, I had an abortion.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.26,0:33:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能休息幾分鐘嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Can you excuse me for one moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.23,0:33:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然可以  稍後繼續為您帶來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Of course. We'll have more of our live interview
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.24,0:33:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與克萊爾·安德伍德的直播訪談\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}with Claire Underwood when we return.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.03,0:33:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那可需要極大的勇氣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That took a lot of guts.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.55,0:33:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes, it did.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.81,0:33:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行  那看上去像是我羞於啟齒\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No. It'll look like I am ashamed.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.02,0:33:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我沒有  我也不會\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm not. And I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.78,0:33:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你再怎麼說都無法挽回\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Nothing you can say will make this any better.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.68,0:33:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我寧願去解決麻煩...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'd rather deal with the dama--
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.36,0:33:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會逃避這個問題\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm not going to run from this.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.70,0:33:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她會問你為什麼要墮胎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She's gonna ask why you had the abortion.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.34,0:33:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不止一次  是三次\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I haven't had one. I've had three.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.06,0:33:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三次  不行  你必須堅稱只有一次\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Three? No. You need to stick to one.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.56,0:33:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Okay, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.57,0:33:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我你要說什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Tell me what you'll say.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.63,0:33:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能說出真相\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, I can't use the real reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.30,0:33:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前兩次我還未成年  我做事不顧後果\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The first two, I was a teenager, and I was reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.54,0:33:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那第三次呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What about the third?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.82,0:33:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那篇她給我看的文章寫得沒錯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, the article that she showed, it's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.88,0:33:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我當時在吃避孕藥\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I was on the pill.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.61,0:34:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但沒有起效果\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It didn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.23,0:34:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們討論過要小孩  最終決定不要了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We talked about having a baby, and then we decided against it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.64,0:34:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.63,0:34:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們在專心忙競選的事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Because we were focused on the campaign.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.56,0:34:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,懷孕多少個星期了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How many weeks in?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.66,0:34:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,16周\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Sixteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.18,0:34:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些你絕不能說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You can't say any of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.92,0:34:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上樓去  我來應付阿什利\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Go upstairs. I'll deal with Ashleigh.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.33,0:34:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果要繼續的話  還有20秒就開始了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If we're going to continue, we've got about 20 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.14,0:34:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,康納  我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Connor, I --
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.76,0:34:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請相信我  不然你會犯大錯的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Please, trust me. You'll be making a big mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.43,0:34:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你願意談談當時的情況嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Are you willing to discuss the circumstances --?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.95,0:34:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的懷孕是一次性侵害造成的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I became pregnant as a result of a sexual assault.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.15,0:34:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是說你被\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Are you saying that you – you were --?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.81,0:34:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,強姦了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Raped.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.73,0:34:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你之前從沒公開說過這件事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You've never spoken about this publicly about this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.84,0:34:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有人過問\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No one ever asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.49,0:34:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能講講發生了什麼嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Can you tell us what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.53,0:34:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是上大學的時候  一個在和我約會的同學\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Uh, it was college. A classmate, we were dating.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.75,0:34:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發生在...有一次我們吵架了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And it happened on a – We had a fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.16,0:34:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後他強暴了我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and he forced himself on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.73,0:35:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和別人說過這件事嗎  他被起訴了嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Did you tell anybody about it, and did he --? Was he charged?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.25,0:35:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有  因為當時我覺得錯似乎在我身上\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No. Because at the time I felt that I was somehow at fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.80,0:35:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道我沒錯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I knew I wasn't,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.88,0:35:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我不想被別人指指點點\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but... just didn't want to be stared at.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.21,0:35:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想別人叫我"被強暴的女孩"\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I didn't want to be known as 'the girl who got raped.'
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.17,0:35:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當發現懷孕的時候  我不想輟學\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And when I became pregnant, I wasn't going to drop out of school.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.47,0:35:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想讓那個男人毀了我的生活\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I wasn't going to let this man ruin my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.50,0:35:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我做出了決定  選擇墮胎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So I made a choice. I ended it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.00,0:35:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果你選擇保持沉默\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But if you never told anybody about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.40,0:35:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罪犯可能還逍遙法外\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}the assailant could still be out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.27,0:35:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能講講關於他的事嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Can you tell us anything about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.24,0:35:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在幾個月前\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I saw him, uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.33,0:35:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時隔三十年  我又見到了他\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}for the first time in almost 30 years just a few months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.30,0:35:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.01,0:35:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在弗蘭西斯和我出席的授銜典禮上\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}At a commissioning ceremony that Francis and I attended.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.66,0:35:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和他說話了嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You speak to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.01,0:35:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說了幾句  弗蘭西斯為他授銜\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Briefly. Francis pinned stars on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.68,0:35:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是授銜者嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He was being commissioned?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.63,0:35:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,道頓·麥金尼斯將軍\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}General Dalton McGinnis.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.73,0:36:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要聲明一下  弗蘭西斯知道那次強姦\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And for the record, Francis has always known about the assault.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.13,0:36:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是不知道名字\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He just didn't know the name.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.35,0:36:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些年來  他一直十分支援我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And he's been nothing but supportive all these years.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.53,0:36:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們得和將軍取得聯繫\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}W—--w--we're gonna have to reach out to the General.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.65,0:36:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看他對你的話作何迴應\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}for a response to what you just said.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.87,0:36:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問我們能不能  稍事休息\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Would you mind if we took a quick break?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.50,0:36:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.49,0:36:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍後繼續克萊爾·安德伍德夫人的訪談\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We'll be right back with Mrs. Claire Underwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.12,0:36:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不著急  慢慢來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Take all the time you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.47,0:36:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,實驗室檢驗結果全是陰性  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The lab tests all came back negative, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.26,0:36:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那玩意是什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.07,0:36:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混了麵粉的滑石粉\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Talcum powder laced with flour.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.88,0:36:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小麥裡的農藥讓檢測呈現假陽性\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It was pesticide from the wheat that gave us the false positive.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.53,0:36:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我們可以走了吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So are we're free to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.61,0:36:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.23,0:36:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-南茜  告訴他們我這就下樓    -已經告知了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Nancy, let them 'em I'm on my way down.   - I already did.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.80,0:36:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-不介意我用你的電話吧    -請便\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Mind if I use your phone?   - Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.35,0:36:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有  唐納德  我會幫你搞到研究資金的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And, Donald? I'm gonna get you that research funding,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.14,0:36:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論投票結果如何\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}no matter how the vote goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.82,0:36:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你自己看著辦  我還是會投反對票    -理解\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- It's your call, because I'm still voting against it.   - I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.00,0:37:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你妻子很勇敢  弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You have a brave wife, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.50,0:37:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你妻子也是  唐納德\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So do you, Donald.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.20,0:37:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Frank!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.35,0:37:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How'd you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.31,0:37:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-還剩四個  布萊斯怎麼樣    -還是不讓步\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- We're down to four. How about Blythe?   - He won't budge.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.70,0:37:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你給了他什麼好處\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What did you offer him?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.49,0:37:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老年癡呆症的研究經費  他覺得這是侮辱\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Alzheimer's research. He was insulted.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.25,0:37:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,投票還有45分鐘就要開始了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The vote's in 45 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.36,0:37:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得聯繫上克萊爾  上車後我該打給誰\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I need to get to Claire. Who should I call from the car?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.51,0:37:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們沒別的辦法了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We've exhausted our options.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.50,0:37:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不說服布萊斯那邊  就通不過投票\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's either Blythe's people, or it won't pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.34,0:37:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們對他太忠心了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They're too loyal to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.23,0:37:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行  去吧  我來解決\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Okay. Go. I'll figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.54,0:37:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果需要我  我可以留下來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I can stay if you need me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.64,0:37:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用  去找你妻子  我知道去哪找你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No. Get to your wife. I know where to find you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.29,0:37:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,南茜  手頭所有的紙都給我  再找些推車\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Nancy, I need every ream of paper you have. And get me dollies.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.47,0:37:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就快完成了  還有20分鐘\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Almost done. Twenty more minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.74,0:37:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭撒謊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I hate lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.94,0:37:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-他做了那事嗎    -做了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Did he do it?   - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.73,0:38:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就別內疚\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Then, don't feel bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.95,0:38:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是他否認了呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What if he denies it?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.96,0:38:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就兵來將擋  水來土掩\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Then we'll cross that bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.01,0:38:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-康納    -再等一分鐘\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Connor?   - Give us one more minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.02,0:38:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有個年輕女人打電話來  是內線\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We have a young woman on the phone, a private.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.25,0:38:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她說她也被將軍強姦了  兩年前\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She says she was also assaulted by the General. Two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.75,0:38:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她想說出她的故事  但不肯透露姓名\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She wants to share her story, but she won't give her name.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.88,0:38:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果她不透露姓名  就不能報道\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We can't put her on if she's anonymous.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.49,0:38:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你想讓我說服她嗎    -她很害怕\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- You want me to convince her?   - She's frightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.76,0:38:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她還線上上嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Is she still on the phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.81,0:38:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒和任何人說過\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I've never told anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.73,0:38:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我過了大半輩子  才有勇氣說起這件事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It took me almost half my life before I could say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.09,0:38:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你現在能說了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But you can say something now.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.75,0:38:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.32,0:38:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想想還可能有多少其他受害者\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Just think of how many others there must have been.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.96,0:38:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你想讓我說出來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But you want me to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.97,0:38:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不想說  就不會打電話了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, would you have called if you didn't want to?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.07,0:38:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒想到還得公開姓名\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I didn't think I'd have to use my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.67,0:38:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽著  我理解你害怕後果\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Listen, I understand you're afraid of the consequence.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.30,0:39:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是個二等兵  而他是將軍\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm a private. He's a general.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.84,0:39:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我丈夫是美國副總統\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And my husband is the Vice President of the United States.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.97,0:39:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們會保護你  我向你保證\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We will protect you. I promise you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.51,0:39:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什麼名字\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.33,0:39:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,二等兵梅根·漢納希\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Private Megan Hennessey.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.73,0:39:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.44,0:39:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一旦開銷凍結\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The names of every person in America
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.48,0:39:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以下所有人就會失去家庭醫保\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}who will lose home care when the Freeze sets in,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.44,0:39:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失去一半的社會福利\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}who will lose half of their welfare benefits,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.52,0:39:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被強迫休假  失去學生貸款\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}who will go on furlough, who will lose their student loans,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.24,0:39:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,交通服務  戰後創傷心理諮詢  還要我繼續嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}transportation services, post-combat counseling. Shall I go on?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.94,0:39:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們得為大局著想  傑奎琳\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This is about the big picture, Jacqueline.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.48,0:39:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個局面我覺得已經很大了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This picture looks pretty big to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.56,0:39:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能投贊成票\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I can't vote for the package.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.76,0:39:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就別投  你們中有四個人就行\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Then don't. Just get four of your people to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.41,0:40:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,避免政府關門後跟我合作\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And then work with me after we avoid the Freeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.33,0:40:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是弗蘭克·安德伍德\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm not Frank Underwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.62,0:40:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那年至少還有另外兩個女孩\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}At least two other girls that same year.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.17,0:40:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果屬實  那麼他服役的這些年來...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If that was true for all the years he's served...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.85,0:40:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太讓人震驚了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's just staggering.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.91,0:40:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且我覺得非常無助\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And I felt so helpless.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.36,0:40:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後他一直晉銜  受到體制的保護\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And he keeps rising in the ranks. The system protects him.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.16,0:40:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得為什麼從來沒有人告過他\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Why do you think no one has ever reported him?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.85,0:40:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想加入嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Do you wanna join her?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.21,0:40:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我們知道根本沒用    -不想\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- We know it won't do anything.      - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.88,0:40:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,官大一級壓死人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Chain of command.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.19,0:40:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你願意出生入死地保衛我們的自由\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's inexcusable that you're willing to put your life on the line
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.09,0:40:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然而你卻無法自由\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}to defend our freedom,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.35,0:40:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說出實情  這實在不可原諒\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and yet you don't feel the freedom to come forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.35,0:40:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我熱愛我的國家\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I love my country.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.25,0:40:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也喜歡在海軍陸戰隊服役\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And I love serving in the Marines.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.30,0:40:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但不是這樣的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But not like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.00,0:40:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,二等兵漢納希  感謝你今晚如此勇敢  接受採訪\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Private Hennessey, thank you for your courage in joining us this tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.44,0:40:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是安德伍德夫人給了我勇氣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It was Mrs. Underwood who gave me the courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.00,0:40:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安德伍德夫人  也感謝你的坦誠\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And, Mrs. Underwood, thank you, for your honesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.45,0:41:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,長官  您夫人來電\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Sir, your wife is on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.94,0:41:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你給了我們很多需要思考的東西\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You've given all of us a great deal to think about.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.59,0:41:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  阿什利\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you, Ashleigh.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.98,0:41:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與克萊爾·安德伍德的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And that concludes our live,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.93,0:41:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,面對面獨家專訪到此結束\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}one-on-one exclusive interview with Claire Underwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.66,0:41:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您可以到我們的網站觀看完整的專訪\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You can watch the entire interview on our website.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.93,0:41:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也歡迎您在臉譜網和推特上\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And, as always, we invite you to give us your thoughts
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.35,0:41:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與我們進行互動\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and your comments on Facebook and on Twitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.80,0:41:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天的專訪就到這兒  感謝收看  晚安\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But, for now, thanks for watching. And good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.52,0:41:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結束\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And we're out.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.04,0:41:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這會引起超出你想像的軒然大波\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This is going to make waves like you never imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.39,0:41:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.14,0:42:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡特呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Where's Carter?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.42,0:42:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你現在向我彙報了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You'll be reporting to me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.76,0:42:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你是誰\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.89,0:42:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡特的上司\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Carter's boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.87,0:42:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘉文  你幹得不錯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're doing good work, Gavin.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.28,0:42:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是你不能對目標動手  那可能會讓我們暴露\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But you can't be assaulting the target. That could compromise us.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.49,0:42:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都不知道為什麼我們要追查這個人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't even know why you're going after this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.32,0:42:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他根本不入流\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He's small-time.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.23,0:42:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是你的事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's not your concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.35,0:42:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他連寫一行程式碼救自己的命都做不到\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He couldn't write a line of code to save his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.12,0:42:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他想發動網路恐怖襲擊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He intends to commit an act of cyber terrorism.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.98,0:42:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那只是個想法  不是能力  他不是真正的威脅\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, that's intention, not capability. He's not a real threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.97,0:42:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許卡特會跟你好言相勸\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Maybe Carter talked things out with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.53,0:42:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.73,0:42:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還要多久\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How much longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.44,0:42:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼多久\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Until what?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.27,0:42:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多久我才能收手\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Until I can stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.65,0:42:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你更想進監獄嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Do you prefer prison?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.95,0:42:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我幫你抓到了八個兒童色情製作者\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I've given you eight child pornographers,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.68,0:42:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三個僵屍網路病毒製造者\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}three botnet masters...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.18,0:42:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是你還是沒有抓到AVunit\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But you still haven't given us the AVunit.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.57,0:42:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我告訴卡特了  我不知道他在哪\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, I told Carter I don't know where he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.80,0:42:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes, you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.82,0:42:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道  誰也不知道\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't. Nobody does.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.73,0:42:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你在Dec-Sec的朋友呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Then what about your friends in Dec-Sec?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.03,0:43:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會讓你動我朋友的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm not giving you my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.55,0:43:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你就幹這個吧  你是個很有用的線人  嘉文\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Then you'll keep doing this. You're a productive asset, Gavin,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.25,0:43:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但等你沒用了  什麼律師也救不了你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but the moment you stop being productive, no lawyer can help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.91,0:43:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是有根真的就好了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Wish we had the real thing right now.
