Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.38,0:44:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真懷念這樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I've missed this.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.25,0:44:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So have I.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.85,0:44:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不應該去接電話  聽別人誇你嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Shouldn't you be on the phone getting your accolades?
